  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_74f27d591e24d6306dd4feb7d60301a7">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Includes correspondence and general and subject files; Cornell Club of Buffalo material; 45th and 50th reunion material of the Cornell University Class of 1917, of which Johnston was secretary; printed material; cancelled checks and checkbooks; and other miscellaneous papers of Herbert Richard Johnston.</p>  </scopecontent>
